item.title: Never mind you helpless bitches
item.dc:creator: @z4mor4k_m1n1on z4mor4k m1n1on
item.description:
@z4mor4k_m1n1on wrote:

ok for ur compiler put
@echo off
COLOR 08
title YOUR SERVER NAME HERE
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\java.exe” server
pause

(supposing u have teh 5.0 9 java JDK update) then go to ur start menu, click my computer then on left hand side of the new window click system information, then click advanced then click enviroment variables and then click new and for ur path put CLASSPATH and then for the one under it put CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin;%CLASSPATH%;. and then click new again and put PATH and under it put C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin and now ur compiler should work
